description: From the Disney Vaults—the original Donald Duck color Sunday comics collected in a book series for the very first time! This premiere volume includes more than three full years of rare Sunday comics, from the first strip on December 10, 1939 through the end of 1942. Drawn by Al Taliaferro and written by Bob Karp, the comics are reproduced from pristine original material in the Disney Vaults!

deck: Showing how the Global Defense Force was formed See how they defended the world against Lotus Mandrake and her Alien Army.
description:
Adam is just like everyone else his age. He had just lost his mother and was selling his family home. On his way back to the University he saw an alien ship crash. Going to investigate Adams body was bombarded with radiation and replaced his nerves with the computer system itself and Manchine was born.

Within the first month of Adam getting his powers he was found out there were other Super Powered Beings like him. A Soldier with super speed and a Teenager with Super Strength, can talk with animals, claws, regeneration and size alterations.

Then the world was turned upside down. A Alien plant race attacked and destroyed Las Vegas. A GIANT tree sprung up in the center of Las Vegas. Manchine and Animal Teen flew to Las Vegas. Animal Teen eaves dropped on a psychic communication between Siege and Sonic Soldier learning where to meet at. Sonic Soldier introduced Manchine and Animal Teen to White Knight and Siege who were from England. They proceeded to stop the Alien plant army. Manchine stopped the horde that erupted from the Tree of Life but this drained him of to much energy causing him to lose consciousness.

Lotus Mandrake defeated the heroes with a paralyzing poison from her skin. Animal Teen seeing this ran away and was buried. Lotus Mandrake believed she had defeated him also. The heroes were connected to the Tree of Life feeding it to seed the Earth. Animal Teen had shrunk down hiding until he couldn't stand it any more and growing to a HUGE size. Knocking Lotus Mandrake through the tree. Animal Teen then proceeded to free everyone except Manchine. Who had been awake listening to Lotus Mandrake and drawing energy from the Tree of Life to power himself back up.

The heroes then faced Lotus Mandrake and using teamwork White Knight was able to behead her. At the end the Tree of Life was about to seed the Earth but Manchine still connected to the tree Manchine Hyperspace jumped the tree from Earth to the sun. He then flew back and was greeted as the Hero who saved the Earth. Manchine started the Global Defense Force so these heroes could be called on to face the challenges that Earth might face in the future.
name: Force Lotus Mandrake vs The World
